longBusinessSummary: Winchester Holding Group, a development stage company, focuses on acquiring and operating rental real estate properties. It intends to acquire single and multi-family real estate and real estate related-assets in the greater Chicago metropolitan area, including Northern Indiana. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Chicago, Illinois.
